data.description:
BEAUTIFUL 5 BEDROOM HOME in VISTANCIA! Fantastic floodplain! 1st Floor has 5th Bedroom and full bath off the entry; perfect for guests or office, Formal Living/ Dining Room, & Great Room with dramatic, soaring, ceilings, that's open to the Kitchen; visit with your guests while you cook! Huge Master W/Sitting Rm! Large Balcony! Home has been recently updated: Remodeled Kitchen & Baths, Freshly Painted Interior/
Exterior, & New carpet in the Great Rm & Bd Rms 2023! Great Freeway access to the 303, then 15 minutes to I17 or 20 Minutes to the I10! This Award Winning Community has excellent Schools & Wonderful amenities, including: Multiple Heated Pools/Spas, water slides,splashpads, tennis, golf, clubhouse, gymnasium, Walking/Biking Paths, & Parks Thru-Out! Move In before the Holidays!
